posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Jay', 'show contact info', 'Description:', 'Studio Apartment | 2009 Bryant Ave S Apt.', '3', '$820', '400 sq.', 'ft.', 'Minneapolis Uptown | The Wedge/Uptown | Lowry Hill', 'KEY FEATURES:', 'Year Built: 1959', 'Parking: Limited Off Street for Rent(check for availability and cost)', 'Lease Duration: 1 Year (See Details Below).', ' 6 and 9 month available at an additional cost', 'Deposit: $500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats Only - limit two, minimum 1 year old, spayed/neutered.', 'Pet Fees: $200 refundable deposit per cat, $20/month pet rent per cat.', 'Laundry: Shared, located in building, credit card operated', 'Utilities: Gas and Trash/Recycling included in rent.', 'Water/Sewer and Electricity are resident responsibility', 'Come home to this quiet and clean 14 unit building.', 'This apartment building is ONE block off Hennepin and the bus line!', 'Just a short walk from all the attractions Uptown has to offer!', 'Enjoy local theatre, restaurants, Bde Maka Ska and Lake of the Isles, Seven Points, Hennepin/Lake, & tons of shopping!', 'Easy bus access to downtown.', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Large Closets', 'Electric Range', 'Refrigerator', 'Air conditioning', 'Cable-ready/Fiber optic-ready', 'LEASE TERMS', '6 month and 9 month leases available for an additional fee.', 'Contact us for questions and showings', 'Owned and Managed by the Hornig Companies.', '<URL>']
